    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips expected from regular driving, while the interior remains comfortable and free of major stains or tears. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has received all scheduled services on time. Buyers can expect a reliable car that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
