      "description": "This exemplary vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, it presents in showroom condition, entirely free from aesthetic or mechanical compromise. Every surface reflects meticulous care, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
